  "texts": [
    "The second aspect was knowing the type of review performed by participants and how long they have been doing it.",
    "The third was to assess the level of ease or difficulty associated with the different stages involved in the SR.",
    "The fourth was to capture the participant's knowledge of AI through automation tools.",
    "Finally, the fifth aspect captured the participants' recommendations for any future AI automation for SR.",
    "The estimated time to complete the survey was 5-10 min."
  ]
